c: 17
v: 12
t: "Ne khwakhola eshilo nende eshitere okhuba ebimanyisio bibili, mana nikhura eshimanyisio shieshilo, ne nikhukhola eshimanyisio shieshitere okhuba nende obulafu kho munyoole tsimbabaasi tsirulanga khu Nyasaye wenyu, ne munyoole okhumanya eshichelo shiemika nende okhubasia. Ne buli eshindu khwashinoosia habulafu"